RESEARCH USE DISCLAIMER

This software and its associated data are intended for research, educational,
and informational purposes only. The Healthcare Dearth Map is NOT a substitute
for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.

The Dearth Scores and visualizations presented are derived from publicly
available datasets (NPPES, Census Bureau, OpenStreetMap) and computational
models. They may not reflect current real-world conditions, including but not
limited to:

- Whether listed providers are actively practicing or accepting new patients
- Appointment wait times or provider availability
- Insurance network participation
- Telehealth or virtual care options
- Sub-county variations in access

The authors make no representations or warranties regarding the accuracy,
completeness, or reliability of the data, scores, or visualizations. Users
should not make healthcare, policy, or business decisions based solely on
this tool without independent verification.

Use of this software is at your own risk.
